decision_details:
- The Hon. Prime Minister brought to the notice of the Cabinet the following programme proposed for the Budget Debate related to the financial year 2023 and the Cabinet granted its concurrence for the said programme.
*	Budget Speech (Second Reading of the Appropriation Bill): 2022‑11‑14;

*	Second Reading Debate (from 2022‑11‑15 to 2022‑11‑22 (07 days);

*	Committee Stage Debate : from 2022‑11‑23 to 2022‑12‑08                 (13 days); and

*	Vote: 2022‑12‑08
